  "text": "where B is the channel bandwidth (Hz), I M is the unity M ×M matrix and ρ is the Signal to Noise Ratio (SNR). The goal of this work is to increase the capacity of the system by proposing a transfer matrix decomposition method inspiring from Radio MIMO channels decomposition [CITATION_1] . This method of system simplification is presented in the next section.",
